  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Receiving, moving, checking and storing incoming goods</p></li><li><p>Checking and inspecting goods received and ensuring they are of correct quantity, type and acceptable quality</p></li><li><p>Selecting space for storage and arranging goods to be placed in designated areas</p></li><li><p>Ensure that daily local delivery orders are fulfilled</p></li><li><p>Assist in arranging delivery of inventory to respective outlets</p></li><li><p>Preparing deliveries for the drivers</p></li><li><p>Picking and packing for export</p></li><li><p>Responsible for checking and ensuring that all shipping requirements/standards are met</p></li><li><p>Ensure goods are always kept neatly on the shelves and in an easily identifiable manner</p></li><li><p>Check periodically and make sure that the needed packaging and cleaning materials are in necessary quantity and quality</p></li><li><p>Delivering stocks to shops and retail outlets when necessary</p></li><li><p>Ensuring a clean and safe workplace</p></li><li><p>Other ad-hoc duties as and when assigned by the management</p></li></ul><p><strong>OTHERS:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Working Location: Penjuru</p></li><li><p>Working Days & Hours: Mondays to Fridays, 830am to 515pm </p></li><li><p>Company provides shuttle bus service.</p></li><li><p>Pick up at Jurong East Bus Pick Up Point at 740am and leaving Penjuru at 515pm.<br /></p></li></ul><p><br />\n\n</p>",
