    "description": "<p><strong>GILLCAPITAL</strong> was established in 2007 by seasoned entrepreneur J.S. Gill. It is a Singapore-based company which operates a group of brands and businesses with world-class credentials.</p>  <p><br /> Building on more than three decades of experience in the Southeast Asian and Middle Eastern markets, Gill Capital cherry-picks the best of global brands and creates innovative retail concepts to give its customers exactly what they want. Sometimes, before they even know they want it.</p>  <p>What the World Wants Next - this springs to mind when describing the ever-expanding constellation of Gill Capital’s stellar brands. From award-winning home-grown concept Candylicious, to fast fashion phenomena H&M, its brands represent the very best of their categories.</p>  <p>Encompassing nine companies and spanning three countries, Gill Capital is a powerhouse of almost clairvoyant creativity, innovation and business acumen Industry observers wonder out loud – what will they do next?</p>  <p> </p> ",
